Hello Richard  Those are the adapter seals . Made so that you can  either put 
an older style type 1 cooler on a newer type 1 case. or a one year  only 1970 
type1 oil cooler to the early small cases . The early oil cooler seals  were 
like a fuel line  ,the same size on both ends.later  mark  dearing
